Package: chd2iso-fuse
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: FUSE filesystem to expose CHD images as ISO/BIN (PS2-friendly)
 chd2iso-fuse mounts a directory of .chd and presents read-only .iso (2048)
 or .bin (Mode2/Form2 2324) files on-the-fly. Useful for PS2 OPL over SMB/UDPBD.

